-- Massachusetts - Boston
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'MA-BOS-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'Boston EMS protocol: CPR, defibrillation, ACLS medications. Consider ECMO for refractory arrest.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Massachusetts - Boston Suffolk' AND c.state = 'Massachusetts' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
